{"tid":1313576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「社會信用體系」— 隨時做左失信人","createTime":"2019-07-13T21:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T21:38:56.000Z","uid":107258,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"23bbe503d2ae50536e3ed7cf5adaf24d10f6300e","tid":1313576,"uid":107258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T21:38:56.000Z","msg":"相信大家呢幾日都有聽過香港要行「社會信用評級」<br />\n評分最低係D級公民<br />\n<br />\n原來除左D級公民<br />\n你可能無啦啦會做左「失信人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n資料會俾法院公告天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑名單仲會有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">懸紅</span></span>等人捉你<br />\n<br />\n分享下港台一條講「社會信用評級」同「失信人」既特輯<br />\n特輯中既第二、第三個案例簡直係痴撚線<br />\n第二個案例<br />\n因為佢曾經同鐵路職員爭執<br />\n佢投訴鐵路職員毫無原因下係身後抱住佢（其實咪即係非禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n所以就被人話佢「影響鐵路安全」<br />\n做埋失信人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第三個案例，受害人俾前夫搞到由「受害人」變「失信人」<br />\n<br />\n點為之失信？<br />\n官方無解釋架，中央話你失信就係失信<br />\n你想請律師？sorry失信人係<span style=\"color: violet;\">無權請律師</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎緊仲會有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全職獵人</span></span><br />\n因為捉到失信人係有懸紅<br />\n微信、報紙、廣告<br />\n全部都有失信人既資料<br />\n<br />\n街邊大電視有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06bzKte.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06bzKte.png&h=af93f231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地係咁e上下wechat都會睇到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b33N4uq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb33N4uq.png&h=a37c9568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xySnTpQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxySnTpQ.png&h=5ce344a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶人包:<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinetekintel.com/blog/2019/07/10/【解讀】用3分鐘了解「社會信用體系」/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinetekintel.com%2Fblog%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F%E3%80%90%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80%E3%80%91%E7%94%A83%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E4%BA%86%E8%A7%A3%E3%80%8C%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E9%AB%94%E7%B3%BB%E3%80%8D%2F&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=8ce68562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinetekintel.com/blog/2019/07/10/【解讀】用3分鐘了解「社會信用體系」/</a><br />\n<br />\n港台特輯:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=share&amp;v=srcGtNTMWvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ffeature%3Dshare%26v%3DsrcGtNTMWvs&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULwVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=d96e92a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=share&amp;v=srcGtNTMWvs</a>"}]}